<h1>How to achieve our objectives</h1>
<ul class="Kompas">
	<li>Presentations on topics of health care and social issues (in the area of mental health), aimed at various target groups.</li>
	<li>Presentations and promotion activities in the area of community mental health care for mental health professionals.</li>
	<li>Výskumná a evaluačná činnosť – monitorovanie rôznych aspektov duševného zdravia obyvateľov a hodnotenie kvality služieb v oblasti duševného zdravia.Research activities – monitoring indicators of mental health and assessing the quality of mental health services.</li>
	<li>Initiate regional, crossing-regional, national and international cooperation in mental health care.</li>
	<li>Participate in existing projects supporting mental health and development of high quality mental health services.</li>
	<li>Develop existing community care services and stimulate creation of community care services where they are needed.</li>
</ul>